316
00:17:47,156 --> 00:17:49,255
Pembicaraan mereka?

317
00:17:49,256 --> 00:17:54,955
Aku sedang memamerkan betapa berkilaunya lencanaku.

318
00:17:54,956 --> 00:17:56,355
Kalau dipikir-pikir,

